{
  "stem": "3165.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my mother said, we have to fall down now, and she covered me up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she told me not to move and-- and not to cry until she tells me when we can go again.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we waited till all the shooting stopped, maybe a little longer yet, til it was all quiet.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother told me, OK, we can run again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she picked me up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we ran again, and we ran away all the way to the village.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Which village?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Korzec.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a small town.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother, again, found the house, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because she knew-- she knew a lot of these people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And she asked if they would hide us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, well, maybe just for a few days, two or three days, because they were scared, too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SIGHS] so here we were at the house, and now she brought my sister, Susan.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and my other sisters were still in a different house, hiding.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, when we were hiding there, it was somewhere in the corner, so no neighbors could see us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because if neighbors would see us, they'd-- they'd report us to the police immediately.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So these people that were trying to protect us had to be very careful as well for their lives.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and my two sisters, Bayla and Leah, were hiding in a different place, which my mother knew where they were.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I don't know how long we were in this house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then one morning, late in the morning, the woman comes up to my mother, and she says, I have bad news for you.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
